org.omnaest.utils.strings
Class StringReplacementBuilder

java.lang.Object
  org.omnaest.utils.strings.StringReplacementBuilder

public class StringReplacementBuilder
extends Object

The StringReplacementBuilder allows to add(String, String) pairs of regEx patterns and their replacement Strings and to process(String) values using these pairs.

Author:
Omnaest
